org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist

Class MusicArtistFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.MusicArtistFactory

  • public class MusicArtistFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains handy method for create music artist artists, loading the details from the disk and for save those to the disk.
